              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "organizations", "{{org_id}}", "objectives", "{{obj_id}}", "approve", ""]
            },
            "description": "**RBAC test.** Uses `{{member_token}}` (a `team_member`) to call the approve endpoint. Only `org_admin` and `team_lead` may approve — the API must return **HTTP 403**.\n\nThe automated test asserts the 403 status and that the error body contains a permission-related message.\n\n**Prerequisite:** Run **Register Second User** and **Add Second User to Org as Team Member** first to populate `{{member_token}}`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
